      "contract": "On each rising crossing of `vclk` through `vth_clk`, sample `vin` and quantize the `0 V` to `1 V` range into eight uniform lower-inclusive bins. Values below `0 V` clip to code `0`; values at or above `1 V` clip to code `7`. Drive `vd2`, `vd1`, and `vd0` as the binary representation of the held sampled code using `vh` for logic one and `0 V` for logic zero.",
